reviewText: In black and white but very entertaining!

Funny stuff. I believe this release has uncut episodes. I have several DVD collections of this show, and the episodes on this DVD are also on one of my other sets. The videos on this DVD are around 10 minutes longer than on the other release.
Bought this as a Christmas present for my stepfather and he was thrilled so I'm thrilled.

What a treat! It is so great to have this compilation of one of the world's best comedy duos. My dad's few smiles came when he saw these episodes, while in bed with dementia. This is a real picker-upper!

I got this and others for my 87 year old Mom. She loves to watch the old shows, it brings back many good memories.
The shows are very good even for the way they had to reproduce it. There not high def, but neither were the originals.
Just good clean humor.
